msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga "
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Catuttharukkhasutta "
msgstr "70. A Tree (4th) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.239, sc1
#. VAR: kūṭasimbalī → koṭasimbalī (bj, s1-3, km) | kūṭasimbali (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci supaṇṇānaṃ rukkhā, kūṭasimbalī tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, of all the trees belonging to the phoenixes, the red silk-cotton tree is said to be the best. "

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāya. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened. "

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyā dhammā? "
msgstr "And what are the qualities that lead to awakening? "

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.4"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati … pe … paññindriyaṃ bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom are qualities that lead to awakening, in that they lead to becoming awakened. "

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci supaṇṇānaṃ rukkhā, kūṭasimbalī tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati; "
msgstr "Of all the trees belonging to the phoenixes, the red silk-cotton tree is said to be the best. "

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.6"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāyā”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.8"
msgid "Bodhipakkhiyavaggo sattamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.1"
msgid "Saṃyojanā anusayā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.2"
msgid "pariññā āsavakkhayā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.3"
msgid "Dve phalā caturo rukkhā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
